 (And how are you, by the way?)</></>CAVIAR, Christianne?  Ohhhhhh!  I&#8217;m swooning a little.</></>Scorpio, sign me up for a flight on Midwest Airlines.  It sounds too good to be true!</></>Magpie Ima, I hear you: I feel a little panicky when I don&#8217;t know where my next (good) meal is coming from.  Amen for frittatas and carrot salads!</p>
